            <title><![CDATA[Bungie's Marathon Has Lost Its Art Director Just Months Before Release]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/bungies-marathon-has-lost-its-art-director-just-months-before-release/1100-6537099/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
